dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Addresses_2018.gdb.[Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.html
